<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="D" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Doctor" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Doctor,</orth> one who has passed the degrees of a faculty, a learned man: <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.5.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. IV, 5, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.4.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 4, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. err 4.4.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Err. IV, 4, 50</bibl> <bibl n="shak. err 5.170.50" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 170</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 3.4.50" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 4, 50</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 105</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 105</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 4.1.105" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 105</bibl> <bibl n="shak. mv 5.210.105" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 210</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. r3 3.5.103" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 III, 5, 103</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.2.122" default="NO" valid="yes">H8 II, 2, 122</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. h8 2.4.206" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 206</bibl>. <cit><quote>--s doubt that,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 5.5.184" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. V, 5, 184</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>but then is an ape a d. to such a man,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ado 5.1.206" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 1, 206</bibl></cit>.<lb />Especially a physician: <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 2, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.4.3" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 3</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.4.3" default="NO" valid="yes">I, 4, 3</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.1.210" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 210</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.3.19" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 19</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 2.3.19" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 3, 19</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wiv 4.4.84" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 4, 84</bibl> etc. <bibl n="shak. 2h4 1.2.1" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B I, 2, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 4.3.145" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. IV, 3, 145</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.1.87" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 1, 87</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.3.37" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 37</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.5.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 5, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.5.30" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 5, 30</bibl>. <cit><quote>your --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. cym 5.2.133" default="NO" valid="yes">Shr. Ind. 2, 133.</bibl></cit> <cit><quote>our most learned --s,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.119" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 119</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>our --s say,</quote> <bibl n="shak. r2 1.1.157" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 I, 1, 157</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>his d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 3.2.317" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. III, 2, 317</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d. She,</quote> <bibl n="shak. aww 2.1.82" default="NO" valid="yes">All's II, 1, 82</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>d. of physic,</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.1.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 1, 4</bibl></cit> (Evans' speech).
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>